    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >• <strong>社区评价</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3100810/extras/4b859d044243edaf09259855e4e71698.avif?t=1751083772\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3100810/extras_big/4b859d044243edaf09259855e4e71698.avif?t=1751083772 width=800 height=228 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3100810/extras/53ac97122e4e305e915002b1342b1887.avif?t=1751083772\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3100810/extras_big/53ac97122e4e305e915002b1342b1887.avif?t=1751083772 width=800 height=176 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3100810/extras/688b5968d1a8ae7a07b2de7cc67f15d9.avif?t=1751083772\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3100810/extras_big/688b5968d1a8ae7a07b2de7cc67f15d9.avif?t=1751083772 width=800 height=204 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《虚幻大圣》是一款以中国神话名著《西游记》为背景的开放世界动作角色扮演游戏。 你将扮演齐天大圣孙悟空，为了消灭从未来穿越而来的妖魔拯救世界，而踏上一条充满危险与惊奇的冒险之旅。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >• 开放世界，自由探索</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >游戏采用虚幻引擎5开发，以超写实的方式构建了一个美轮美奂的奇妙开放世界。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >广袤而精致的游戏世界等待你的探索，地图充满了令人惊叹的细节和隐藏的宝藏。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3100810/extras/e15b40123340a1edd492838c81c0852c.poster.avif?t=1751083772\" width=700 height=394 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3100810/extras/e15b40123340a1edd492838c81c0852c.webm?t=1751083772\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3100810/extras/e15b40123340a1edd492838c81c0852c.mp4?t=1751083772\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3100810/extras/0e728e59233a9f4fbd937104ffe7f154.poster.avif?t=1751083772\" width=700 height=394 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3100810/extras/0e728e59233a9f4fbd937104ffe7f154.webm?t=1751083772\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3100810/extras/0e728e59233a9f4fbd937104ffe7f154.mp4?t=1751083772\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3100810/extras/3def549197f760cdc396b50c2d0fa977.poster.avif?t=1751083772\" width=700 height=394 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3100810/extras/3def549197f760cdc396b50c2d0fa977.webm?t=1751083772\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3100810/extras/3def549197f760cdc396b50c2d0fa977.mp4?t=1751083772\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >•齐天大圣，降妖除魔 </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >齐天大圣，威名远扬。部分西游记中家喻户晓的妖魔悉数登场，与大圣展开激烈对决。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3100810/extras/1c569d956455e0eb4011909cd14c72c8.poster.avif?t=1751083772\" width=700 height=394 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3100810/extras/1c569d956455e0eb4011909cd14c72c8.webm?t=1751083772\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3100810/extras/1c569d956455e0eb4011909cd14c72c8.mp4?t=1751083772\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3100810/extras/0b39f4edf16284575493544fbd39791b.poster.avif?t=1751083772\" width=700 height=394 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3100810/extras/0b39f4edf16284575493544fbd39791b.webm?t=1751083772\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3100810/extras/0b39f4edf16284575493544fbd39791b.mp4?t=1751083772\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >• 如意神棒，法力无边 </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >金箍棒可伸缩自由，远程与近战自由选择。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >孙悟空拥有瞬息移动、铜头铁臂与72般变化等法术傍身，对战敌人游刃有余。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3100810/extras/ead5c565b7fad1b811b97f82e6a338a8.poster.avif?t=1751083772\" width=700 height=394 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3100810/extras/ead5c565b7fad1b811b97f82e6a338a8.webm?t=1751083772\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3100810/extras/ead5c565b7fad1b811b97f82e6a338a8.mp4?t=1751083772\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3100810/extras/04c3c79b98adfca5897e362d08a21b6d.poster.avif?t=1751083772\" width=700 height=394 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3100810/extras/04c3c79b98adfca5897e362d08a21b6d.webm?t=1751083772\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3100810/extras/04c3c79b98adfca5897e362d08a21b6d.mp4?t=1751083772\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3100810/extras/fa4be00c415cd327ac74f6e1d09462d7.poster.avif?t=1751083772\" width=700 height=394 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3100810/extras/fa4be00c415cd327ac74f6e1d09462d7.webm?t=1751083772\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3100810/extras/fa4be00c415cd327ac74f6e1d09462d7.mp4?t=1751083772\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >• 装备系统，角色成长 </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >通过战斗不断提升悟空的能力，解锁新的技能和装备。打造独一无二的齐天大圣。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3100810/extras/bd65a002136b7183515bbae4735f789a.poster.avif?t=1751083772\" width=700 height=394 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3100810/extras/bd65a002136b7183515bbae4735f789a.webm?t=1751083772\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3100810/extras/bd65a002136b7183515bbae4735f789a.mp4?t=1751083772\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><i><u><a href=\"mailto:客服邮箱：3826103835@qq.com，任何问题与建议都可发邮件联系我们。\">客服邮箱：3826103835@qq.com，任何问题与建议都可发邮件联系我们。</a></u></i></h2>",
